<h2 id="section-top">Neurology</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=27">Barking, Havering and Redbridge University Hospitals NHS Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent5159deeb0ea24b3eacd45aba79256add">
</div>
<p>Neurology is a branch of medicine dealing with disorders of the nervous system.<br/><br/>Our consultants diagnose, treat, and manage patients with neurological disorders. They are also involved in clinical research, clinical trials, as well as basic research and translational research.</p>
<p>Â <a href="http://www.bhrhospitals.nhs.uk/copy_of_our-services/neurosciences.htm">Please click here to visit our extensive Neurosciences website</a></p></div>
